GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 1st May, 1956.
The undersigned is direct ed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that Shri Mono Mohan Das assumed office
as Deputy Minister with effect from today, the 1st May, 1956
(forenoon). He will be attached to the Ministry of Education.
Aseni
(A.S. Gill)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
